react

Class RQueue<E>

  • java.lang.Object
    • react.Reactor
      • react.RCollection<E>
        • react.RQueue<E>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Iterable<E>, Collection<E>, Queue<E>

    public class RQueue<E>
extends RCollection<E>
implements Queue<E>
    Provides a reactive model of a Queue. Note: unlike standard Java queues, reactive queues do not support removing arbitrary items from the queue; only the head of the queue may be removed.
